	(517,51,'tips','<em><strong>Tip:</strong> If you keep the butter in the refrigerator or freezer and don\'t want to wait for it to come to room temperature, use a cheese grater to shred the sticks into your mixing bowl before you start. Prepare the dry ingredients in another bowl while you wait and after 5-10 minutes the butter should be soft enough to work with.</em>'),
